Abuja (Sundiata Post) – There is a wide fire raging in Ijegun, a Lagos suburb. Residents said it was caused by some pipelines vandalised by hoodlums. “Everywhere is on fire. We’re all outside with our properties. We can’t go to work because the fire is huge,” a resident, Adeola Adekoya said. He called for emergency responders to mobilise their men to Ijegun. Details Shortly…